dct_title_s: Map of the Jumel, Murray, Burrall, Dickey and other estates : showing the farm lines, roads, lanes, streets, &c. as they exhisted [sic] 100 years ago and the present streets, drives and boulevards
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Also shows locations of old buildings and original shoreline and drainage. Relief shown by hachures. "Copyright by J.B. Holmes, 1887." Oriented with north to the upper left. Hand colored. Includes text.
dct_publisher_sm: [New York : City Surveyor], c1887 (N[ew] Y[ork] : Robert A. Welcke, Photo-Lith.)
